Вакансія від 2 березня 2020
Retention Manager
15 000 – 20 000 грн
Vigo Group
IT;
50–250 співробітників
Київ
Повна зайнятість.
Досвід роботи від 1 року.
Опис вакансії
An iGaming company is looking for highly motivated individual to run Retention campaigns.Key responsibilities:• Design and execution of Retention promotions, campaigns.• Communication with inactive customers via phone, email, messengers to make them active users again.• Making sure clients get the best experience using our brands.• Quick, polite and accurate answering to customer requests and enquiries.• Provision of players with information on all promotions they are eligible for,new games, rules amendments, etc.• Assisting players with any technical issues they might have, because of which they stopped use the product• Close cooperation with product team, suggesting special service improvements for players, based on feedback from clients.Candidate requirements:• At least 1 year of experience as an Account Manager/Customer Support Representative in gambling industry.• Perfect spoken and written English.• Passion for customer relationship management and commercial awareness.• Self-motivation, reliability and ability to work independently.• Focus on customer needs and good customer service skills.• High communicative abilities and patience.What you get:• Working in a friendly team, favorable for professional growth.• Opportunity of career development.• High salary and additional benefits.
